        <div class="prose">
          <p>Render's managed platform simplifies deployment but the cost per compute unit is high relative to VPS options. At $25/mo you get 2GB RAM on a shared CPU — not enough for comfortable Dify operation. Running the full Dify stack on Render requires a higher-tier plan, pushing costs well above alternatives. Render works for Dify but it's hard to recommend when cheaper options exist.</p>
